[% PageVersion = 'root/Documentation/DailyPlans/DailyPlans-2026-01-13.tt,v 1.02 2026/01/13 23:30:00 zencoder-bug-fix Exp - Jan 13 Daily Plan RESTORED: Fixed bug from previous chat - restored Today Work tab content, AI Instructions section, Completed tab details, app todo list include. Verified ApplicationTtTemplate.tt compliance.' %]
