                <li><strong>Preserve Tab Structure:</strong> Never remove existing tabs without explicit user permission. You may add new tabs, but do not delete TODAY'S WORK, RESOURCES & CONTEXT, AI WORK INSTRUCTIONS, or COMPLETED tabs.</li>
                <li><strong>Update Within Containers:</strong> Edit task content within task-list containers, not the containers themselves. Preserve checkbox structure and task items.</li>
                <li><strong>Link to Master Docs:</strong> Reference PriorityTodos.tt at /admin/documentation/PriorityTodos - never duplicate the full table into daily plans.</li>
                <li><strong>Track Progress:</strong> Update checkbox status as tasks complete. Move items to COMPLETED tab when done.</li>
                <li><strong>Conditional Planning:</strong> If a critical blocker succeeds, update the next day's plan to show unblocked work.</li>
                <li><strong>Log Changes:</strong> After edits, document changes in both PageVersion comment and COMPLETED section.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Tab Structure (DO NOT CHANGE)</h3>
        <ul style="line-height: 1.8;">
            <li><strong>Floating Header:</strong> Sticky position with navigation. Date, status, links to Master Plans, All Docs, Todo System, Previous/Next day</li>
            <li><strong>Tab 1: TODAY'S WORK</strong> - Current day focus area with master plan priorities and app todo list from application. Includes action items and recommendations.</li>
            <li><strong>Tab 2: RESOURCES & CONTEXT</strong> - Supporting documentation links, quick links, and space for daily notes</li>
            <li><strong>Tab 3: AI WORK INSTRUCTIONS</strong> - Guidelines for AI agents working on this plan. Includes DailyAuditGuide content. This tab.</li>
            <li><strong>Tab 4: COMPLETED</strong> - Items completed today, moved from TODAY'S WORK when finished. Should include detailed task breakdown with results.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

